column5: Hello everyone, My name is Nadeel, and I'm from Toronto. I love fishing. I also buy and sell new and used fishing tackle. Last year I was able to purchase a handful of items at a good deal and I want to pass on the savings to you guys and girls. I love fishing hopefully we can meet up and fish someday. In the mean time, lets share stories and pics and maybe you will also be interested in some of the items for sale. Thanks for reading....PEACE!!
